@startuml API Logs Plugin Interface

!theme crt-amber
left to right direction

title IFluxionLogsPlugin Interface and Methods

package "Fluxion::API::LogsPlugin" {
    interface IFluxionLogsPlugin {
        + GetDisplayName(): string_view
        + OnEnable(OnEnableData): void
        + OnDisable(OnDisableData): void
        + RenderMenuLayer(): void

        + ImportLogs(path): void
        + GetTableHeader(): vector<ColumnDetails>
        + GetTotalLogs(): size_t
    
        + ApplyFilters(filters, highlight_only): void
        + DisableFilters(): void
        + GetLogs(ranges, out_logs): void

        + GetNextLog(filter_id): optional<size_t>
        + GetPrevLog(filter_id): optional<size_t>
    }
}

note right of IFluxionLogsPlugin
  Factory function: CreateFluxionLogsPlugin()
  Responsible for:
  - Log I/O operations
  - Filtering and searching
  - Column-based rendering
  - Navigation through filtered logs
end note

@enduml
